gurmukhi: ਜਾਪ ਕੇ ਜਪਿੰਦਾ ਖੈਰ ਖੂਬੀ ਕੇ ਦਿਹਿੰਦਾ ਖੂਨ ਮਾਫ ਕੇ ਕੁਨਿੰਦਾ ਹੈ ਅਭਿੱਜ ਰੂਪ ਠਾਨੀਅੈ ॥
transliteration: Jaap Ke Japindaa Khair Khoobike Dihindaa Khoon Maaf Ke Kounindaa Hai Abhijj Roop Thaaneeai||
translation: He is cause of the repetition of His Name and Giver of peace and hounour; He is the forgiver of the blemishes and is considered as Unattached.

gurmukhi: ਅਾਰਜਾ ਦਿਹਿੰਦਾ ਰੰਗ ਰਾਗ ਕੇ ਬਢਿੰਦਾ ਦੁਸਟ ਦ੍ਰੋਹ ਕੇ ਦਲਿੰਦਾ ਛੋਡ ਦੂਜੋ ਕੌਨ ਮਾਨੀਅੈ ॥੭॥੪੬॥
transliteration: Aarjaa Dihindaa Ran Raag Ke Badhindaa Doust Droh Ke Dalindaa Chhodh Doojo Kaoun Maaneeai||7||46||
translation: He is the prolonger of life, the Promoter of the entertainments of music and the masher of tyrants and malevolent, whom else should we then ADORE? 7.46.

gurmukhi: ਅਾਤਮਾ ਪ੍ਰਧਾਨ ਜਾਹ ਸਿੱਧਤਾ ਸਰੂਪ ਤਾਹ ਬੁੱਧਤਾ ਬਿਭੂਤ ਜਾਹ ਸਿੱਧਤਾ ਸੁਭਾੳੁ ਹੈ ॥
transliteration: Aatmaa Pradhaan Jaah Siddhataa Sarooptaah Buddhataa Bibhoot Jaah Siddhataa Soubhaau Hai||
translation: His Self is Supreme, He is Power-incarnate, His wealth is His Intellect and His Nature is that of a Redeemer.

gurmukhi: ਰਾਗ ਭੀ ਨ ਰੰਗ ਤਾਹਿ ਰੂਪ ਭੀ ਨ ਰੇਖ ਜਾਹਿ ਅੰਗ ਭੀ ਸੁਰੰਗ ਤਾਹਿ ਰੰਗ ਕੇ ਸੁਭਾੳੁ ਹੈ ॥
transliteration: Raag Bhina Ran Taah(i) Roop Bhina Rekh Jaah(i) An Bhisuran Taah(i) Ran Ke Soubhaau Hai||
translation: He is without affection, colour, form and mark, still He hath beautiful limbs and His Nature is that of Love.

gurmukhi: ਚਿਤ੍ਰ ਸੋ ਬਿਚਤ੍ਰ ਹੈ ਪਰਮਤਾ ਪਵਿਤ੍ਰ ਹੈ ਸੁ ਮਿਤ੍ਰ ਹੂੰ ਕੇ ਮਿਤ੍ਰ ਹੈ ਬਿਭੂਤ ਕੋ ੳੁਪਾੳੁ ਹੈ ॥
transliteration: Chitra So Bachitra Hia Parmataa Pavitra Hai Su Mitra Hoon Ke Mitra Hai Bibhoot Ko Oupaau Hai||
translation: His painting of the universe is Wonderful and Supremely Spotless; He is friend of friends and Supreme Donor of wealth.

gurmukhi: ਦੇਵਨ ਕੋ ਦੇਵ ਹੈ ਕਿ ਸਾਹਨ ਕੋ ਸਾਹੁ ਹੈ ਕਿ ਰਾਜਨ ਕੋ ਰਾਜੁ ਹੈ ਕਿ ਰਾਵਨ ਕੋ ਰਾੳੁ ਹੈ ॥੮॥੪੭॥
transliteration: Devak Ko Dev Hai Ki Saahan Ko Saah(u) Hai Ki Raajan Ko Raaj(u) Hai Ki Raavan Ko Raau Hai||8||47||
translation: He is the god of gods monarch of monarch; He is the king of kings and chieftain of the chiefs.8.47.
That Lord is Indestructible; that Lord is Indivisible.
That Lord is Formless; that Lord is Griefless.1.48.
That Lord is Unassailable; that Lord is Indiscriminate.
That Lord is Nameless; that Lord is Desireless.2.49.
That Lord is Guiseless; that Lord is Accountless.
